1. **Identified the issue**: The test `com.fasterxml.jackson.core.json.TestJsonParser::testGetValueAsTextBytes` was failing because when the parser was positioned on a `FIELD_NAME` token, calling `getValueAsString()` was returning `null` instead of the field name text.

